o-600x297.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All this helps ensure you know which pages are indexed so you can better troubleshoot those that haven’t been indexed.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-2-optimize-your-sitemaps\">2. Optimize Your Sitemaps</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want search engines and users to find your posts and pages easily, you must create an optimized XML sitemap.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"535\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-1024x535.png\" alt=\"Example of XML sitemap\" class=\"wp-image-185484\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-1024x535.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-300x157.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-768x401.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-600x313.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-115x60.png 115w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap-172x90.png 172w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/example-xml-sitemap.png 1323w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>These help search engines crawl and understand your URLs better, resulting in better indexing. Don’t worry if you have lots of pages on your site. AIOSEO makes it easy to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-multiple-urls-to-your-sitemap-the-easy-way/\" title=\"How to Add Multiple URLs to Your Sitemap (The Easy Way)\">add multiple URLs to your sitemap</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"345\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-1024x345.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO makes it easy to add multiple URLs to your sitemap.\" class=\"wp-image-99835\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-1024x345.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-300x101.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-768x259.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1-600x202.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/add-multiple-urls-to-additional-pages-1.png 1038w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>When you submit your sitemap to Google Search Console (GSC), you can easily monitor your URLs for performance and identify potential issues impacting your SEO.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For more details, we’ve created a handy guide to help you <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/create-a-wordpress-xml-sitemap-without-a-plugin/\" title=\"How to Create a WordPress XML Sitemap Without a Plugin\">create sitemaps in WordPress</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-3-leverage-the-indexnow-protocol\">3. Leverage the IndexNow Protocol</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-indexnow-for-seo/\" title=\"What is IndexNow for SEO (Explained in Plain English)?\">IndexNow protocol</a> makes the internet more efficient by instantly alerting participating search engines of any changes you make on your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"270\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/indexnow-activated.png\" alt=\"The IndexNow protocol helps your content get indexed faster.\" class=\"wp-image-73093\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/indexnow-activated.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/indexnow-activated-300x116.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/indexnow-activated-600x231.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, if you change your content or add a new post or page, the IndexNow protocol will ping search engines about those changes.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Doing so will result in the search engines crawling and indexing your changes faster.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This means IndexNow is a powerful tool to help you get your content indexed faster, resulting in better chances of ranking.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another significant advantage of IndexNow is that if one search engine participating in the IndexNow initiative is pinged, all other search engines will be alerted when new content is published. As a result, your content will quickly appear in search results for relevant searches.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best part is that <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-indexnow-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Add IndexNow in WordPress (For Faster Indexing)\">adding IndexNow to your site</a> is easy.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-4-optimize-your-robots-txt-file\">4. Optimize Your Robots.txt File</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-robots-txt-in-wordpress/\" title=\"What is Robots.txt in WordPress? [Beginner’s Guide]\">A robots.txt file</a> is a powerful SEO tool that guides search engine crawl bots or robots on which pages to crawl. As you may have guessed, it’s important that your robots.txt gives Google permission to crawl most of your site.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the other hand, it’s common to disallow wp-admin pages and other pages irrelevant to your SEO strategy. That’s because they aren’t useful to your search strategy. Telling Google not to crawl unnecessary pages can help boost rankings in search engines and increase page speed.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"280\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/aioseo-robots-txt-file.png\" alt=\"Example of a robots.txt file\" class=\"wp-image-26295\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/aioseo-robots-txt-file.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/aioseo-robots-txt-file-300x115.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/aioseo-robots-txt-file-600x230.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But when it comes to indexing in SEO, you should ensure your important pages are crawlable. You can tell Google bots to allow crawling and even prioritize these URLs.&nbsp; This is super easy to do with <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/robots-editor/\" title=\"Robots.txt Editor\">AIOSEO’s Robots.txt Editor</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"502\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO\'s robots.txt editor.\" class=\"wp-image-222049\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1-300x215.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1-600x429.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1-84x60.png 84w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-easily-edit-a-robotstxt-file-in-wordpress-1-126x90.png 126w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This powerful tool makes optimizing your robots.txt file easy as it comes with many useful directives such as Allow, Disallow, Clean-param, and Crawl-delay.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives.png\" alt=\"Directives in AIOSEO\'s Robots.txt Editor.\" class=\"wp-image-220372\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives-300x182.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives-600x364.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives-99x60.png 99w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-directives-148x90.png 148w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You also have the option to import a robots.txt file from another site, saving you a lot of time optimizing yours.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"321\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import.png\" alt=\"Importing a robots.txt using AIOSEO.\" class=\"wp-image-220390\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-300x137.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-600x274.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-131x60.png 131w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/how-to-edit-robots-txt-import-197x90.png 197w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For more details, please visit our post on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-edit-a-robots-txt-file-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Easily Edit a Robots.txt File in WordPress (Step by Step)\">how to edit a robots.txt file in WordPress</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Enhancing your site’s indexing is super important to ensuring your content ranks and driving relevant traffic to your site. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>For more tips, check out our article on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/index-your-website-on-google/\" title=\"10 Quick &amp; Easy Ways to Index Your Website on Google\">easy ways to index your site on Google</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-indexing-your-faqs-answered\">What is Indexing? Your FAQs Answered</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-does-indexing-mean-in-seo\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What does &#8220;indexing&#8221; mean in SEO?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>In SEO, indexing refers to the process in which search engines organize and store information gathered during the crawling phase. It involves creating an efficient catalog of web pages, making it easier for search engines to retrieve relevant results when users perform a search query.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-why-is-seo-indexing-important\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Why is indexing in SEO important?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>SEO indexing is crucial for visibility in search engine results. Well-indexed content is more likely to appear in search results, improving the chances of attracting organic traffic. It enhances the user experience by delivering relevant and timely results.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-are-there-tools-that-can-help-with-indexing\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Are There Tools that Can Help With Indexing?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Yes. Tools like All In One SEO (AIOSEO) can help ensure that your site and pages get indexed. It has features like IndexNow, an advanced robots.txt editor, and much more.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-improve-your-indexing-boost-your-rankings\">Improve Your Indexing, Boost Your Rankings</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know what indexing is and why it’s important, go ahead and optimize your site for indexing by search engines. Remember, with AIOSEO, you get a lot of features and tools to help you do that.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you understand what indexing is and why it’s important for your SEO. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-content-optimization-tools-for-seo/\" title=\"7 Best Content Optimization Tools for SEO\">top content optimization tools</a> or our guide on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/crawl-cleanup-best-practices/\" title=\"How to Use Crawl Cleanup to Increase Search Engine Crawl Quota\">using Crawl Cleanup to boost your SEO</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter)</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/indexing-in-seo/\">What Is Indexing in SEO? A Beginner’s Guide [Plus Tips]</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"https://aioseo.com/indexing-in-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		